::Bazooka::

    He could see the back of Waspinator and Shredder. He lifted his Axe/gun. 
He aimed it just right. 
    "Set for attach grenade." Bazooka muttered to the gun. "I hope Shredder 
doesn't get in the way."
    He pulled the trigger and the grenade launched. It found it's way to 
Waspinator's back.
    "There, he shouldn't be able to reach that." Bazooka said. "Shredder, 
duck and cover!" He yelled out.
